node.text:
Make the getaway without leaving home.

We built an original, custom, Wowie-themedTiki Hut, and you can win it! No purchase is necessary, all you have to do is text “TROPICABANA” to 55678 for a chance to win. It's a tropical staycation!

You must be 21 to enter. Open to legal residents of  IL, IN, KY, OH, PA, TN, and WI. Employees of Rhinegeist Brewery, suppliers, distributors, or retailers of alcohol-beverage products and their immediate family members are not eligible to enter. Happy Friday!
We’re proud to be a participant in this year’s @alesforals . Ales for ALS is a national fundraising campaign created in 2013 by a Yakima Valley hop farming family to raise funds and awareness for ALS, or Lou Gehrig’s disease. Each year @loftusranches and @yakimachief donate a unique hop blend, developed by master brewers, to select breweries across the country.

This year’s blend includes Simcoe, Sabro, Mosaic, Citra, Talus, Equanot, and several others. The resulting brew is all about showcasing this diverse, citrus-forward hop bill, and is brimming with orange, pineapple and herbal notes.  $1 from every pint is donated to @alstdi . Our Ales for ALS brew is pouring in the taproom now!

#cincymade #AlesforALS

The power of perception.
Aged in an oak foeder for 12 months with our house cultures before a healthy addition of passionfruit, Perceptual Passion acquires mild funk, tart acidity and pronounced tropical fruit character. Gold medal winner at the 2018 @fobab in Chicago. Perceptual Passion is a very limited release, available on draft and in 500 mL bottles.

For the team.
Hop-forward beer drew many of us to craft in the first place, especially the West Coast styles that were popular when we opened, making Double IPA the perfect style for us to celebrate our transition to employee ownership. Employee Owned is a West Coast Double IPA that we absolutely loaded with our favorite American hops. Notes of resinous pine, zesty grapefruit, and freshly cut grass are highlighted by an assertive bitterness and just a hint of crackery malt. To get the deets on this righteous IIPA, head over to the latest Beer Review (link in bio).

100% of all profits from Employee Owned will be donated to @whw_empower 
 
#cincymade #teamwork #hopdividends
